{"tid":337462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［樣板戲］傳廣電總局下令　全國戲院須預留45%場次放映《建軍大業》","createTime":"2017-07-27T10:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T13:58:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f20235ebcd0280a4674881292bc131dba1afdb0","tid":337462,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"香港導演劉偉強的作品《建軍大業》周五首映，廣電總局下令要求全國戲院預留近半場次放映。<br />\n<br />\n為慶祝中國共產黨建軍九十周年而製作的《建軍大業》，將於明日上映。據 Hollywood Reporter 報道，廣電總局上周發出通知，要求國內影院預留最少 45% 的場次作放映《建軍大業》之用。有不願透露姓名的連鎖影院經理表示，預留 45% 檔次「相當難做」，擔心周末票房收入會大受影響，「希望可以減低至少於四成」。<br />\n<br />\n《建軍大業》屬於「建國三部曲」系列，是繼早前《建國大業》、《建黨偉業》之後的新作，主要敘述 1927 年的南昌起義，被視為「紅戲」之一。電影先於明日在大陸上映，並於下周來港上畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%BB%A3%E9%9B%BB%E7%B8%BD%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%A0%88%E9%A0%90%E7%95%99%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E5%A0%B4%E6%AC%A1%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0-%E5%BB%BA%E8%BB%8D%E5%A4%A7%E6%A5%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B1%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A5%25AD%2F&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bf8c0596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B1%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A5%25AD%2F&h=1fd94272\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%BB%A3%E9%9B%BB%E7%B8%BD%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%A0%88%E9%A0%90%E7%95%99%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E5%A0%B4%E6%AC%A1%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0-%E5%BB%BA%E8%BB%8D%E5%A4%A7%E6%A5%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"fc72063461e12dda4e0d37c01cb9525c95793af3","tid":337462,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"全國包唔包括西九總站同圓方？"},{"pid":"bb6750237561f39098a6afdb213ee9910a433f6f","tid":337462,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全國包唔包括西九總站同圓方？</blockquote><br />\n全國梗係包埋全港"},{"pid":"4674f89dc20ed822c4319631accf884a7b407b0d","tid":337462,"uid":56657,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://1.blog.xuite.net/1/b/8/a/17149096/blog_755782/txt/26891841/0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.blog.xuite.net%2F1%2Fb%2F8%2Fa%2F17149096%2Fblog_755782%2Ftxt%2F26891841%2F0.jpg&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a17cb0eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://1.blog.xuite.net/1/b/8/a/17149096/blog_755782/txt/26891841/0.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"a47966d1716d34132bcd2b68da4bcb5d29980141","tid":337462,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://1.blog.xuite.net/1/b/8/a/17149096/blog_755782/txt/26891841/0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.blog.xuite.net%2F1%2Fb%2F8%2Fa%2F17149096%2Fblog_755782%2Ftxt%2F26891841%2F0.jpg&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a17cb0eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://1.blog.xuite.net/1/b/8/a/17149096/blog_755782/txt/26891841/0.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0590667d671ee0fdeeab2ce5b7